  <brief_title>Reduced Intensity Transplant in Medically Refractory Systemic Lupus Erythematosus (SLE) and Systemic Sclerosis (SSc)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Reduced Intensity Conditioning And Allogeneic Stem Cell Transplantation in Patients With Medically Refractory Systemic Lupus Erythematosus and Medically Refractory Systemic Sclerosis (SSc)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
